# Maven Job

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Manage Jenkins -> Global Tool Configuration:

JDK -> JDK installations -> JDK -> Name: Java_1.8 + JAVA_HOME: /usr/lib/jvm/java-1.8.0-openjdk-amd64/jre
Maven -> Maven installations -> Maven -> Name: mvn + MAVEN_HOME: /opt/maven

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Install "Maven Integration Plugin"

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Create a new Maven Job

Source Code Management -> Git -> Repositories -> Repository URL: https://github.com/xavyaly/game-of-life.git
Credentials: NA

Branches to build -> Branch Specifier (blank for 'any'): */master

Build -> Root POM -> gameoflife-build/pom.xml
Goals and options: compile package

Save 

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
